## Example Application

`com.verisign.vscc.hdfs.trumpet.client.example.TestApp` is a sample application, listening to Trumpet and finding `_SUCCESS` files, 
indicating the success of a MapReduce application. 

It would be really easy to start a distcp job from here to, for instance, replicate the resulting data into a different cluster.


